Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.91,0:00:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions \Nthat will make the night sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:12.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you enjoy tonight's miracle, \Nin which red and white intersect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:26.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm being serious! Keiko saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was studying in the library yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already this late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:45.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one should still be upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:06.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened to Keiko after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so shocked that she stayed in bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:17.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the only thing to do is avenge her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:09.46,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,15,,{\fad(1000,0)}Adult's Charm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to go with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's dangerous for \Na cute girl to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,School at night gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and apparently Keiko isn't the \Nonly person who's seen a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,11 people have seen one this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them were students \Nwho stayed here late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll be 12 and 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"13" is an unlucky number to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't talk like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A speaker... The broadcasting room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's yankin' my chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens \Nwhen you run in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito, you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it definitely wasn't my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's trying to scare us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just a prank? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'll leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go you with in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:51.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh! Scream, and they'll \Nknow where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit whimpering!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You only {\i1}treat{\i0} me like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for leaving me in the lurch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Don't leave me alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on, it's a man's area!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let a girl be exposed to danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How cliched...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. If they come in, give me a shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come charging over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in you, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito! Hurry up... Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.71,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Science Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}is{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I do them here in the science \Nroom after everyone else has gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty of space in here,\N and a lot of chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do stuff that can be\N taken the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:49.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't you dare breathe \Na word about this to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell people, then they'll also find out\N that you're Kid the Phantom Thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, I'm not \NKid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:01.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake, Nakamori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:06.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any ghosts. It was just Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I do magic experiments here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, magic! Akako wants to \Nlearn how to do magic tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't sneak around here to \Ndo it! Next time, I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in learning \Nyour tricks whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magicians are a witch's mortal enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's why I said, "It's me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still got scared and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guilty as charged! Sorry, Akako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too tired to take care \Nof you if you faint again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you really are a little kid, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what does he see \Nin that childish girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets my blood boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This? It's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A charm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:32.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Akako-chan \Nwas just telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-chan, sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I teach you a charm \Nthat'll make you more like an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.12,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Adult
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:49.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is write "adult" on your \Npalm and wrap a handkerchief around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But listen. You have to \Nleave it on for four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the bathtub, you can't wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know how to be a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I {\i1}am{\i0} a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do this charm yourself, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:16.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that "charm" is nonsense! \NI just want her to look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Kuroba Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men everywhere are captive to my charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their gaze falls on me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:29.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So how? How can you ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should... You should \Njust vanish permanently!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. I should rid this world of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:46.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the rest of the men \Nwill all be my slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:51.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I didn't \Nthink of this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be too good-natured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroba Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just suddenly got a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-sama, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the rest of your short life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Most wicked god of this world, Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:29.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal your misshapen form \Nand answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Lucifer! Come before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:47.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? \NWhat fool would dare summon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, answer me, Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I bring an end \Nto Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of a full moon, the \Ncriminal will make a path in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:02.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and hide in a tall, crimson tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, that gives me orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was it. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you made what I requested?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, in order to continue being a magician,\N there is something you must never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a child's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you realize that, \Nyou'll be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A child's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be 17 this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been an adult for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Everyone's in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.49,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Emperor's Golden Seal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Don't shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him captured alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kid! This'll be the \Nnight I finally catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A full moon tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I let you in on a \Nlittle secret, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the night \NKid the Phantom Thief dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Where were you \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Where I go is my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill that little turd full of lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna push Kid off this mortal coil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird! What's wrong with \Nthe inspector tonight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of a full moon, the criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will make a path in the sky and \Nhide in a tall, crimson tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Kuroba Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the end result will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're dead, you'll be nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:12.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're trying to steal my life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:18.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the ever-elusive Kid the \NPhantom Thief. I can even fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe you can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And adults are much stronger than children!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even wipe you off the \Nface of this Earth right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it! Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't need you to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults are strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the beautiful gem lying \Ndeep within your frozen heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wipe anyone off \Nthe face of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're still a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:30.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There, see? You {\i1}are{\i0} a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch. I got a scrape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're on tiptoes, trying to \Nbecome an adult, only looking at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're talking about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:51.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe there's nothing wrong \Nwith staying a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:09.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On tiptoes, trying to become an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheesy line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. Guess I'll secretly return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You consider yourself an adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:38.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you wet the bed and \Ncry for "Mommy" when you fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in recent memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you're an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be more composed \Nand less talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.\N I recently had to laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to a new pancake \Nhouse with a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What {\i1}is{\i0} an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe him out! Wipe him off \Nthe face of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.56,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Emperor's Golden Seal Stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe this out! Wipe that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wipe everything out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The charm that'll make you an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:21.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Like I'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting embarrassed about it is \Nmore proof that you're a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm a kid, you're a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are still children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The charm to become an adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, until next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May you never forget the \Nheart of a child, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone sends Aoko an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:37.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for a private dinner at the \NBell Tree Tower, which sounds great,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:39.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently, there's a catch to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, we get mixed up\N in trouble, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the past and present converge, the \Nfirst Kid the Phantom Thief appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Enter: The Phantom Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:53.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter: The Phantom Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
